long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Installing The Cat Tab extension allows you to replace default browser new tab background with a wallpaper with cute cats.

Features:

- Choose new tab cats wallpaper as your favorite
- Speed dial with most popular sites
- Handy search bar

By clicking "Add to Chrome", I accept and agree to installing The Cat Tab and setting New Tab to that provided by the service and the Terms of Use and Privacy Policy. The extension will change your New Tab services provided by The Cat Tab.

Terms of Service: https://thecattab.com/terms.html
Privacy Policy: https://thecattab.com/privacy.html
